Class ParseFilter.FilterResult

java.lang.Object
org.zaproxy.zap.spider.filters.ParseFilter.FilterResult
Enclosing class:
ParseFilter
public static final class ParseFilter.FilterResult extends Object
The result of a ParseFilter's check.

Used to indicate if a resource was filtered and why.

Since:
2.7.0
